  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK992">
<l>aṉpuṭaimai yāṉṟa kuṭippiṟatta livviraṇṭum</l>
<l>paṇpuṭaimai yeṉṉum vaḻakku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Affectionateness and birth in a good family, these two constitute what is called a proper behaviour to all.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
